  "title": "Aviation Specialist, Design and Engineering (A105)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Industry:</strong> Commercial Aviation Industry</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Location:</strong> East area</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Schedule:</strong> 5-day work week</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>This position will be joining an established Singapore Aviation Company in the business of Commercial Aircraft servicing, support and maintenance.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The primary function of this role is to lead in the design and development of nacelle related systems such as inlet, anti-icing, thrust reverser, electro-mechanical and acoustics technology.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Position Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Will be responsible and involved in designing and development of nacelle systems (eg: inlet, thurst reverser), ascertain safety and repairability, maintenance and certification.</li>\n  <li>Planning testing and validation of design solutions as well as providing design improvement and technical repairs.</li>\n  <li>Lead a team of Design Engineers within Singapore and other countries.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Position Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Aerospace Electronics, Aerospace Avionics.</li>\n  <li>10 years working experience in Aerospace / Aviation sector with strong background in nacelle design, development and testing.</li>\n  <li>Knowledge in FAA/EASA/CAAC regulations on nacelle and propulsion systems.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We will look into all candidates but will prioritize those closest to the requirements.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Thank you!!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Joseph Syho</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Reg Number: R1108657</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA Licence No.: 18C9079</p>",
